law.text:
KRS 304.13-011 to 304.13-161 apply to all types of insurance written on risks in this state by any insurer authorized under this chapter to do business in this state, except:
Life insurance;
Annuities;
Wet marine and transportation insurance;
Accident and health insurance;
Reinsurance;
Assessment or cooperative companies operating under the provisions of KRS Chapter 299;
Individual and group workers' compensation self-insurers;
Title insurance; and
Liability self-insurance groups.
